snippet.title: Tape 101 Official Announcement Trailer | Wishlist on Steam
snippet.description:
Wishlist "Tape 101" on steam, link is in the comments bellow !

Tape 101 is an indie psychological horror adventure game about the backrooms, where you will explore liminal spaces and solving puzzles to get your way through, the game play is focused on walking around exploring, and using an RC-Car to navigate through unexplored places that the player can't reach also the RC-Car will help the player collect some items to solve the puzzles in the walk through.
